sprint_goal: Establish the core calculator, user registration, and login functionality with legal compliance foundations.
Implement the Ohm's Law calculator, enable secure account deletion, and build the foundational offline capability for the core calculator.
Deliver the 555 Timer Astable mode, begin the custom mode feature with the creation wizard, and implement robust offline data synchronization.
Complete the custom mode creation logic with formula writing and execution, implement GDPR/CCPA data export, and enhance user onboarding with a guided tour.
